---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Free llms.txt Generator | Rank4AI" description="Generate your llms.txt file in 2 minutes. The emerging standard for communicating directly with AI search platforms.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Tools', href: '/learn/tools/' },
      { label: 'Llms Txt Generator' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Free Tool</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Free llms.txt Generator</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">llms.txt is an emerging standard - a structured file at your domain root that communicates directly with AI systems what your site is and where its most important content lives. Only 13% of UK SME websites have one.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This tool helps you generate a basic llms.txt file for your website. Fill in your business details and it creates the file structure for you.</p>
    <div class="bg-off-white border border-border rounded-xl p-8 mb-10">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">What Goes in llms.txt</h2>
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-sm text-text-muted">
        <pre class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-xs">
# Your Business Name
# https://yourdomain.com

Company Name: Your Business Name
Location: Your City, Country
Industry: Your Industry
Focus: What your business does

Primary Services:
- Service 1
- Service 2
- Service 3

Core Pages:
Homepage: https://yourdomain.com
Services: https://yourdomain.com/services
About: https://yourdomain.com/about
Contact: https://yourdomain.com/contact

Contact:
https://yourdomain.com/contact
        </pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Save this as <code class="bg-off-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">llms.txt</code> in your website root directory. For a dynamic, auto-updating version like ours, <a href="/contact/" class="link">contact us</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/learn/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Resources</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Guides</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
